long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the future with the Cyberpunk McLaren live wallpaper, bringing a high-tech, neon-filled supercar to your Chrome new tab.

The Cyberpunk McLaren Live Wallpaper combines the sleek, futuristic design of McLaren with a cyberpunk aesthetic, immersing you in a world of neon lights and speed every time you open a new tab.

Features:
Cyberpunk McLaren Live Wallpaper
Google search bar
Addable and removable shortcuts
Date and time display

This Chrome extension pairs an eye-catching chrome wallpaper with practical tools for seamless browsing. As one of the top chrome live wallpapers, it enhances your chrome background with both style and functionality.

For more live wallpapers, explore Gameograf.com. Discover extensions like: Ferrari Cyberpunk Live Wallpaper, Lamborghini Neon Live Wallpaper, Porsche Futuristic Live Wallpaper, Bugatti Electric Live Wallpaper, Aston Martin Hypercar Live Wallpaper.
